parameters: Kru "This one is... the legendary monster... the Giant Frog!!"
Umi "Hm? You know this huge frog?"

Kru "You don't know, Umi?! This creature is a monstrous beast that has
devoured countless adventurers!"

Kru "Yeah... According to legend, at times it has devoured wizards... at
times holy knights... and it's even said to have preyed upon goddesses...
To encounter it here..."
Umi "If that's the legend, maybe we can get some tasty meat from it."
Kru "What are you saying! Let's escape right now!"

Umi "What are you talking about. Kru is strong. Umi is strong. Meat is
delicious. There's nothing to fear. Let's hunt it quickly!"
Will you battle the Giant Frog?
Umi "For the meat! I'll do my best!"
Kru "No good! We need to escape quickly before it attacks!"
Umi "Hmph... and here I thought we could get some delicious meat."
Umi: "Haa haa... So this is the legendary monster..."

Kru: "Ahh, but we've weakened it considerably... Still, it seems impossible
to defeat. Let's escape while we can..."
Umi: "No! We're going to defeat it and eat its flesh!"
Kru: "Damn it... Don't you... lay a hand... on Umi..."
Umi: "No... I don't want this... Don't eat me..."

My body was covered in the Giant Frog's saliva, and the terrible stench was
overwhelming. But the fear of death was so great that I hardly noticed the
foul smell.
Umi: "...No! It's slimy and feels disgusting..."

I deeply regretted ignoring Kru's warning and desperately trying to deliver
the final blow to the Giant Frog. If only I hadn't been so greedy then...

Umi: "What's with this tongue sensation... And the way it's moving isn't
like it's trying to eat..."
Umi: (What's with this frog... What does it want...)

Umi: "Ahh... I'm starting to feel hot... Could it be that my clothes are
dissolving...?"
Umi: "No! Stop it... Don't dissolve them..."

How long have I been licked? My clothes have completely dissolved, and now
I'm drowning in the Giant Frog's maw, naked as the day I was born.

No matter how much I pleaded, the Giant Frog kept persistently licking my
body. The initially unpleasant sensation of its mucous membrane and its
warmth had become almost comforting.
Umi: "Ahh... haa haa... Somehow... Umi is feeling strange..."

How many times have I looked at Kru, who won't wake up? How many times have
I imagined him suddenly rising to defeat this large, hideous monster?

However, I had long since given up on such an impossible dream. This
monster could easily swallow both of us in one gulp. The fact that it
doesn't simply means that, in the eyes of this creature, the battle had
ended long ago.

All that's left is for it to toy with us before consuming us. That's all
there is to it.

Umi: (No... When it licks my crotch, I shiver... Is this frog deliberately
avoiding that spot while licking?)
Umi: (No... I don't want to feel this way from a frog like this...)

Umi (There's no mistake... this frog... it knows that spot is sensitive...
What kind of frog is this...)

As expected of the legendary monster that has buried many adventurers in
darkness, I was convinced by this creature's use of its tongue. How many
humans has it toyed with using its tongue?

I let out a sigh of admiration for the delicate movements of the tongue
that one would hardly expect from such a large body. The chief used to say
that a true powerhouse could be both strong and gentle, but I could only
feel resignation at the gap between the strength and rhythm of this
creature's ministrations below.
If only it would swallow me whole in one go.
Umi (No... Why did I let out such a voice...)
Umi "Aaahhh! It's intense! No... I don't want this..."

It's finally happening... I thought. Surely this monster must have grown
tired of licking me all over.
Umi: "As expected of the legendary frog..."
Kru: "What's wrong! Are you challenging the Giant Frog?"

Umi: "Eh... no... I don't really understand, but... we should probably
stop..."

Umi: (Eh? What was that? It feels like I was having a strange dream... I
can't remember, but... it was a very bad dream...)
